OL,6,FAround 220 people living in Jersey are
OL,7,Fhomeless, according to a first-of-its-
OL,8,Fkind government report.
OL,10,FThe Homelessness in Jersey Report
OL,11,FSecond Quarter 2024 compiles data from
OL,12,Fhomeless charities and service
OL,13,Fproviders to identify the extent of
OL,14,Fhomelessness on the island.
OL,16,FIt comes after Housing Minister Deputy
OL,17,FSam Mezec launched a project to
OL,18,Fimprove the collection of evidence of
OL,19,Fhomelessness on the island.
