OL,6,FAt risk, experience of, or escaping
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse was the main recorded
OL,8,Freason for homelessness among females
OL,9,Fin 39% of cases.
OL,11,FSubstance abuse was the main recorded
OL,12,Freason for homelessness among males -
OL,13,Faround 14% of cases.
OL,15,FThe report states that those who were
OL,16,Fhomeless were predominantly between 26
OL,17,Fand 65 years of age.
OL,19,FHowever, there were 17 young people
OL,20,Frecorded as homeless in this quarter.
