OL,6,FHousing Minister Deputy Sam Mezec,
OL,7,Fsaid: "For a number of years, there
OL,8,Fhas been a lack of meaningful data
OL,9,Favailable regarding the situation in
OL,10,FJersey regarding homelessness. This
OL,11,Fhas made it hard to fully and
OL,12,Faccurately understand the scale and
OL,13,Fnature of the issue in Jersey.
OL,15,F"The reporting of this data will
OL,16,Fprovide a deeper understanding of the
OL,17,Flevel of demand on different providers
OL,18,Fand how they respond to the issue of
OL,19,Fhomelessness.
