OL,6,FThe Minister added data will allow the
OL,7,Fgovernment to: "Develop a broader,
OL,8,Fricher, deeper understanding of this
OL,9,Fissue so that informed and useful
OL,10,Fpolicy can be created to tackle the
OL,11,Fissues surrounding homelessness.
OL,13,F"It is, however, always important to
OL,14,Fremember that behind the statistics,
OL,15,Fthere are many individual stories, and
OL,16,Fwe must always remember the very human
OL,17,Fnature of this issue."
